<h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  " id="details-title">Details</h2>


<div aria-labelledby="details-title">
  
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>Following its inquiry into Brexit and local government, the Housing, Communities and Local Government Select Committee (<abbr title="Housing, Communities and Local Government">HCLG</abbr>) <a rel="external" href="https://publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm201719/cmselect/cmcomloc/493/493.pdf">published a report (PDF, 330KB)</a> setting out 10 recommendations for government.</p>

<p>This document sets out the governmentâ€™s response to these recommendations.</p>

